description:
As one of the most-visited cities in Europe, Edinburgh is known for its whisky heritage, striking architecture, and intriguing history. Not to mention its beautiful natural scenery and buzzing pub scene. The city is big enough that youll be entertained, but compact enough that you can explore everything on foot. In this video, we highlight 10 of the best things to do in the city, which are best combined in a 3 to 4 day visit.
